snippet.title: Best VGM 655 - Pokemon XD : Gale of Darkness - Miror B! Battle!
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube
Pokemon XD : Gale of Darkness (2005)
Miror B! Battle!
Tsukasa Tawada
